        "text": "🚨 **Negative Review Alert** ({{ $json.rating }}/5 stars)\n\n**Business:** {{ $json.business_name }}\n**Author:** {{ $json.author_name }}\n**Review:** {{ $json.text }}\n\n**AI Response Draft:**\n{{ $json.ai_response_draft }}\n\n_Sentiment Score: {{ $json.sentiment_score }}/5_",
